{"tid":1974580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當局推健身中心資助計劃　每中心獲10萬元一次性津貼","createTime":"2020-04-16T02:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T16:32:09.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5b9f3c69b359b760911302f2396876264ca656","tid":1974580,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"抗疫基金推健身營運資助 每所健身中心獲10萬津貼<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情重挫香港經濟，加上港府上月28日起實施「禁聚令」，關閉包括健身中心在內的6類娛樂場所，令健身中心經營困難。民政事務局今(15日)表示，為協助健身中心因暫停營運所引致的財政困難，政府將於第二輪「防疫抗疫基金」下推出「健身中心資助計劃」，以紓緩疫情帶來的影響。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200415/bkn-20200415195801231-0415_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200415%2Fbkn-20200415195801231-0415_00822_001.html&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=311fa805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200415/bkn-20200415195801231-0415_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1389a92b7096e4ec5d3496952af1c4bab209e29b","tid":1974580,"uid":74990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"教練慘慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e542f21eda96f29a6c9eb92c9c04f557f2f9da","tid":1974580,"uid":74990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"我可包養教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac83123210e96da90b5025531aa0278f1384e3c","tid":1974580,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"一次性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劏一個水魚三十年會籍都唔止啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然都應該有小數唔劏良心但係唔太知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb32392af62e14ecb5f0c9702a294539ab57da00","tid":1974580,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:32:09.000Z","msg":"睇來考DSE真係大過天，甚至比促進經濟發展更重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全香港市民要因為DSE而繼續無得做gym/yoga、唱K、睇戲、去酒吧、一大班人聚餐派對等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n禁聚令於文憑試開考前夕屆滿 政府大機會延2周至5月初<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1978355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1978355</a>"}]}